memory_text = "LEENA SHAH: 'Read only what someone here can vouch for.' Rafi reads thirty-one names. A second voice corrects two spellings and refuses a third. Nobody calls the list complete. At the bottom Maggie has written: ELLIE WARD - LAST SEEN CULLBROOK - UNCONFIRMED."
